  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with 6.5%≤HbA1c≤11.0% at screening

          -  Subjects treated with 1,000mg/day or higher dose of metformin for at least 6 weeks
             prior to screening among people treated with metformin monotherapy for at least 12
             weeks before screening

          -  Subjects with 20kg/m2≤BMI≤40kg/m2 at screening

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with fasting plasma glucose≥270mg/dL at screening

          -  Patients with type 1 diabetes mellitus, secondary diabetes mellitus or gestational
             diabetes mellitus

          -  Subjects with history of myocardial infarction, cerebral infarction within 6 months
             prior to screening

          -  Subjects with ALT and AST 2.5 times or higher than upper normal range
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
